{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, boost, marti-common-msgs, marti-nav-msgs, rclcpp, swri-geometry-util, swri-math-util, swri-roscpp, swri-transform-util, tf2-geometry-msgs, visualization-msgs }:
